## Dependencies
```
- Python >= 3.9  
- PyTorch >= 2.0.1  
- PyTorch-CUDA >= 11.8  
- NumPy >= 1.26.4  
- Pandas >= 1.5.3  
- SciPy >= 1.10.0  
- Scikit-learn >= 1.5.2  
- tqdm >= 4.66.1  
- Matplotlib >= 3.9.4  
- Seaborn >= 0.12.2  
```
---

For **PyTorch installation**, we recommend users to follow the official [PyTorch installation guide](https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/) to select the correct build based on their CUDA version.

